The following folder contains file to run SCDV with polysemy corpus

Directory Structure : 

* data : contains the 20NewsGroup data along with polysemy word corpus 

* adagram_julia : Contain the code for annotating sense using adagram (not yet updated due to licence)

* Word_Vectors : Contains the code to create word embeddings

* Word_Topic_Vectors : Contains the code to create word topic vectors with redcution code 

* SVM_classifier : Code to run the linear SVM on the generated embeddings

* CNN : code to run the CNN experiment on the generated word embeddings


Run the codes in the following order : 

Adagram -> Word_vectors -> Word_topic_Vectors
then either SVM_classier or CNN . 

